# EDA

## 체중과 물칼퀴 관계


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
penguins %>% 
  ggplot(aes (x = flipper_length_mm, y = body_mass_g,
              color = species)) +
    geom_point() +
    labs(x="물칼퀴", y="체중")+
    facet_wrap(~island)
```

